snippet.title: Youth Went to Deposit Banned Notes, Dies Outside Bank in Bareilly

localized.description:
Youth went to deposit banned notes, dies outside bank in Bareilly.
Peoples are struggling to exchange and deposit currency notes of Rs 500 and Rs 1000 after Modi government demonetisation decision. In Parliament winter session TMC, Congress, Left, BSP, SP and AAP are attacking Modi government over inconvenience of peoples.
